<title>THS's Guide</title>

<p style="margin-top: 1cm; font-size: 250%;">Karis's DrakeNieR Timeline</p>
<p id="title1">Updated on June 3rd, 2026.</p>
<p id="title2">All sources will be listed per entry.</p>
<p id="title3">Note: A large portion of this timeline is translated from <i>Accord's Library</i>, and a select amount of re-translations done by me.</p>


<style>
div {
  text-align: left;
}
.para{
  margin-left: 10%;
  margin-right: 10%;
}
@media screen and (orientation: portrait) {
  .line {
    margin-top: 6.5%;
  }
  .para u a {
    margin-top: 5%;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .para {
    font-size: 135%;
    text-indent: 0em;
}
}
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  .special-color {
    border: thick solid rgb(58, 58, 58);
    background-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);
  }
}
@media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
  .special-color {
    width: fit-content;
    margin-right: auto;
    border: thick solid rgb(201, 201, 201);
    background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  #timeline-meta{
    font-weight: 1.25rem;
    color: rgb(42, 42, 42);
}
}
#no-indent {
  text-indent: 0em;
}
#title-small {
  font-size: 15%;
}
#timeline-meta{
    font-weight: 1.25rem;
    color: rgb(156, 156, 156);
}
.timeline-container{
    display: grid
}
.Guide {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
}
</style>
<div class="over">
<div class="Guide">

<div class="timeline-div">
<p class="title-special title-box" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"><b>1</b></p>
<p class="title" id="timeline-meta">World Inside - Chronology</p>
<h3 class="title">Birth of Christ</p>
</div>

<div class="timeline-div">
<p class="title-special title-box" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"><b>4</b></p>
