<h3 class="title">Outbreak of the Second Germanic War</p>
</div>


<div class="timeline-div">
<p class="title-special title-box" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"><b>30</b></p>
<p class="title" id="timeline-meta">World Inside - Chronology</p>
<h3 class="title">Death of Christ</p>
</div>

<div class="timeline-div">
<p class="title-special title-box" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"><b>64</b></p>
<p class="title" id="timeline-meta">World Inside - Chronology</p>
<h3 class="title">Great Fire of Rome</p>
<p class="para">Persecution of Christians by the tyrannic Emperor Nero.</p>
</div>

<div class="timeline-div">
<p class="title-special title-box" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"><b>100</b></p>
